Anambra State College of Health Technology (ASCOHT), Obosi bụ ụlọ ọrụ ọzụzụ ọkachamara na ọtụtụ ọzụzụ nke dị n'obodo Obosi di na Idemili North Local Government Area, Anambra State

Kọleji ahụ na-achịkwa site na ụlọ ọrụ Naijiria maka agụmakwụkwọ teknụzụ NBTE, Radiographers Registration Board of Nigeria, Medical laboratory Science Council of Nigeria ọkachamara Boards na-achịkọta ụlọ ọrụ tertiary na Naijiria nke o nwere ikike zuru oke n'okpuru provost Dr
E guzobere Anambra State College nke Health Technology, Obosi na 1992 mgbe e guzobere steeti Anambra nke oge a na 1991 n'okpuru nduzi nke Chukwuemeka Ezeife
N'afọ 2001, e guzobere ya site na iwu nke Anambra State House nke Assembly ANHA / LAW/2003/2 iji zụọ ike nwoke dị mkpa na ngalaba ahụike maka steeti, ọrụ nlekọta ahụike nke mbụ na nke abụọ.
